 explained if CO2 becomes the main contributor for the three\n[OI] lines at high heliocentric distances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Oct 2012 16:53:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Apr 2013 13:40:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
