ir estimated specific surface angular momenta, a subgroup of stars exploding\nin this phase may represent an evolutionary channel towards LGRBs at high\nmetallicities, comparable to the Galaxy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Oct 2012 15:45:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Oct 2012 14:47:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
